text: Kampong Bebatik is a settlement in the south-western part of Brunei-Muara District, Brunei. It is officially a village-level subdivision under the mukim (subdistrict) of Sengkurong. The postcode for Kampong Bebatik is BH3223. == Name == Kampong Bebatik comes from the Malay name which translates as 'Bebatik Village'. It is named after , the Brunei Malay word for golden trevally (Gnathadon speciosus). == References == Bebatik
